cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.CL 

The paper deals with deep learning-based image retrieval, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks (cs.MM) and fine-tuning (cs.LG) for the task. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of a loss function (cs.CL) for deep metric learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.IR, followed by cs.MM, cs.LG, and cs.CL.
